text: Godelieve Brys (born 24 April 1937) is a Belgian gymnast. She competed in five events at the 1960 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1937 births Category:Living people Category:Belgian female artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Belgium Category:Gymnasts at the 1960 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Aalst, Belgium
